        <h3>About Retort</h3>

        <p>
          Retort is a collection of natural language generation APIs for easily adding and maintaining natural language in your applications. A set of API endpoints allow for incredibly easy markov chain generation, stimulus response, and other language generation tasks. 
        </p>

        <h3>Proudly powered by <a href="http://indentlabs.com">Indent Labs</a></h3>
